This repo is associated with my blog post [Explorint IoT Information Exchange Patterns with Azure Service Bus and Gadgeteer](http://christoferlof.com/blog/2014/8/9/exploring-iot-information-exchange-patterns-with-azure-service-bus-and-gadgeteer)

This sample shows how Azure Service Bus can be used as an intermediary service to connected devices in order to simplify concerns regarding security, addressing and messaging reliability.